snippet.title: Key: Maze of Illusions - Walktrough / Level 1 (Siene Games)
snippet.description:
Level 1 Walkthrough of the Key: Maze of Illusions game!

Gameplay made in hard mode, but works in any other mode.

Remember that this is just one method of passing, there are more than one and that can vary according to the taste of the game.

We hope you have helped, any other questions, suggestions or requests, you can send us and we will respond right away :)


• Steam Page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/16...

• Play Store Page: https://play.google.com/store/apps/de...

• Siene Games on Twitter: https://twitter.com/siene_games

• Siene Games on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/SieneGames/

• Siene Games on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/sienegames/

Come venture into a dangerous dungeon full of enemies and deadly traps with Key: Maze of Illusions! An insane and addictive platform action game. Help Zeno find the keys he needs to explore all the rooms in the dungeon and find out what really happened!
